I was in the hotel lobby, waiting on my driver & just minding my business...when this gorgeous soul says “Now you look faaaabulous… I love it! “ & it just happened to be THEE @bevysmith THEE Queen of fashion, trust me you’ll be lost for words too! 😆 

Especially when you’ve fought breast cancer the last 2 years, had a double mastectomy, treatments, & 5 surgeries later ( last one only 42 days ago) Its so challenging fighting to live …but many don’t understand the battle physically, mentally, financially and emotionally! As a woman,  it’s often hard to sustain your confidence & sexy during & after this process! Your compliments & love toward me made my day! You never know how your words & presence blesses folks! When you’re outside…Be present, be intentional & be kind even in passing!! Thank you Ms Foxy B! Hope to see you again!
